SingPost Says Baier to Be Group CEO, Names Ng as CFO

-- B y   L i n u s   C h u a
-- 
2011-10-05T09:39:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/singpost-says-baier-to-be-group-ceo-names-ng-as-cfo.html
Singapore Post Ltd. (SPOST)  said it appointed
Wolfgang Baier as group chief executive officer as it steps up
efforts to become regional company.  Baier held the position of CEO international. Ng Hin Lee,
who was CEO of of postal and corporate services, will be chief
financial officer, SingPost said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Linus Chua at 
 lchua@bloomberg.net  